            <title><![CDATA[【[二哈]#穿阴干的衣服可能引发哮喘荨麻疹#】一起床，头发像刚洗完！可怕的#回南天#它又来了[裂开] 专家提醒，衣服长期阴干，人体处于潮湿环境中，比较容易滋生...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%A9%BF%E9%98%B4%E5%B9%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%E8%8D%A8%E9%BA%BB%E7%96%B9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%A9%BF%E9%98%B4%E5%B9%B2%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A3%E6%9C%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%E8%8D%A8%E9%BA%BB%E7%96%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#穿阴干的衣服可能引发哮喘荨麻疹#</span></a>】一起床，头发像刚洗完！可怕的<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%97%E5%A4%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#回南天#</span></a>它又来了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 专家提醒，衣服长期阴干，人体处于潮湿环境中，比较容易滋生真菌、细菌等微生物，出现异味，并且可能导致哮喘、荨麻疹等感染性疾病和过敏性疾病👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5008193005486116" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hnew7rpmgmj20u01hcacv.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/9yVjhbotlx08d1eK3Lyg01041200eQrj0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709629707&amp;ssig=BouxeHiOgU&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3OwahmVklx08d1eKtbDi0104120083O50E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709629707&amp;ssig=t3%2BegqWnd3&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/pAVklQ6Tlx08d1eJT6K4010412004ohS0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709629707&amp;ssig=y4WHEHWbyH&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5008193005486116" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
