            <title><![CDATA[【🤳🏻#总看手机会加速得白内障吗#】医生介绍，白内障主要病因是晶状体老化，目前没有确切依据证明看手机会加速白内障形成。从临床看，白内障严重到需要手术...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🤳🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%80%BB%E7%9C%8B%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%BE%97%E7%99%BD%E5%86%85%E9%9A%9C%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%80%BB%E7%9C%8B%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%BE%97%E7%99%BD%E5%86%85%E9%9A%9C%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#总看手机会加速得白内障吗#</span></a>】医生介绍，白内障主要病因是晶状体老化，目前没有确切依据证明看手机会加速白内障形成。从临床看，白内障严重到需要手术的患者大多以六七十岁为主。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BB%B6%E7%BC%93%E7%99%BD%E5%86%85%E9%9A%9C%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%BB%B6%E7%BC%93%E7%99%BD%E5%86%85%E9%9A%9C%E5%8F%91%E7%97%85%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#如何延缓白内障发病时间#</span></a>？建议避免高强度紫外线照射、糖尿病患者有效控制血糖等👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5001607423918093" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hmtvsnp6x3j615o1jkqv502.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/anaI8bftlx08cyfqp2so01041200qlCj0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709629707&amp;ssig=v9DxOTCoKc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/PDQ1I3PMlx08cyfq346A01041200fo6P0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709629707&amp;ssig=4GL4UhFSph&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/km3kC6YDlx08cyfpTUas0104120081DT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1709629707&amp;ssig=06C4AmlPIf&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5001607423918093" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
